{"tid":2434674,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"TQQQ信念區，先買為敬","createTime":"2021-03-05T16:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T09:49:15.000Z","uid":265395,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"77b1bc0deb0a8ac336420241babe99da97e00ca7","tid":2434674,"uid":265395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"實在唔忍心見到連登一片愁雲慘霧，決定身體力行，入貨支持股市，重拾昔日光輝!<br />\n<br />\n買TQQQ原因如下:<br />\n<br />\n1. 有三倍槓桿，可以快啲追返之前輸嘅錢。<br />\n<br />\n2. ETF已分散風險，大市回升佢實升，好過你沽注一擲，買中千年妖股就無得翻身。<br />\n<br />\n3. 長遠股票市場必升，呢個係上至股神，下至傻散同共嘅信念，亦都係事實。所以SH TQQQ無得輸，只係唔知要等幾耐。<br />\n<br />\n4. 只要唔好做孖展，咁就算跌都可以安心坐，因為你知道一定升返。買個股就日日瞓唔著，因為真係可以升唔返。<br />\n<br />\n想追返數嘅就慢慢入返TQQQ啦"},{"pid":"e2b7b958a7fb450b8b2a7e538b373adc57da6ccd","tid":2434674,"uid":265395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c89srsZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc89srsZ.png&h=94d155aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bb08423f72c2b68aca1bcbfad244090d091cd4b","tid":2434674,"uid":77186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"而家？ 有冇時間值"},{"pid":"f86b8617ebb76d71f9787611108db89e1033aa00","tid":2434674,"uid":314357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"唔否定你嘅信念 不過可能早咗少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b399f7da4ef3b65eeb28786d7dbebbd4df763cfe","tid":2434674,"uid":124983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:37:35.000Z","msg":"入soxl<br />\n豬緊30％<br />\n但照樣訓得著<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8263da9c28ade66ad45892f417ecf5385f446c14","tid":2434674,"uid":265395,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f86b8617ebb76d71f9787611108db89e1033aa00","tid":2434674,"uid":314357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"唔否定你嘅信念